    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Step into the spotlight of a deadly spectacle 　 welcome to The Beautiful Life Show.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A horror action adventure crafted in side scrolling, old school fashion, this game thrusts you into the starring role of a bizarre and unforgiving performance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your stage? A nightmarish theater of death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal? Survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259730/extras/982fcb04b87884a2206e29dde5e937af.avif?t=1758252459\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>At the heart of the experience lies the innovative Death-Sense Action.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When death claims you, time rewinds　just three seconds back, but enough to rewrite fate. Collaborate with the ghost of your former self, reliving your final moments in tandem to outwit traps, overcome foes, and press onward into the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you endure to the final curtain and dare to peer into the abyss that lies beyond?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259730/extras/02ec96e41727c80a2e396151977949f1.poster.avif?t=1758252459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259730/extras/02ec96e41727c80a2e396151977949f1.webm?t=1758252459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259730/extras/02ec96e41727c80a2e396151977949f1.mp4?t=1758252459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
